Elyssa Davalos https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elyssa_Davalos 0 Elyssa Davalos (born May 30, 1959) is a former American television and movie actress. Her father is actor Richard Davalos. She is the mother of actress Alexa Davalos, from her marriage to photographer Jeff Dunas. She is of Spanish and Finnish descent on her father's side. Her family name would be spelt originally "Dávalos" in Spanish, with an accent on the first "a". Elyssa_Davalos ( born May_30_,_1959 ) is a_former_American_television_and_movie_actress .
